{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-20523/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-20523"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["2:05:23"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Credits on a black background."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-20523","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-20523"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1/3acc0f86-0e5d-45b6-9f3f-4cb55aad632c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T13:32:45.422Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The credits end with a dedication to director Jonathan Demme, one of PTA's early influences and eventual friend and mentor. On PTA’s relationship with the director, see Ellie Palmer’s “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW139842121 BCX4\" href=\"https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/the-jonathan-demme-movie-that-changed-paul-thomas-andersons-life/\"><u>The Jonathan Demme movie that changed Paul Thomas Anderson’s life</u></a>,” Richard Whittaker’s “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW139842121 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.austinchronicle.com/screens/2018-03-02/paul-thomas-anderson-on-his-friendship-with-jonathan-demme/\"><u>Paul Thomas Anderson on His Friendship With Jonathan Demme</u></a>,” and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW139842121 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RXT0WOUceak&amp;t=1s\"><u>this conversation</u></a> between the two filmmakers from the Austin Film Festival. Beyond how PTA borrowed from Demme’s technical repertoire, the latter’s influence can be felt in how unrestricted by genre and conventions PTA is. Like Demme, he has directed musical performances and shorts for <em>Saturday Night Live</em>. PTA spoke about his relationship with Demme and his work with Terry Gross on <em>Fresh Air</em> (Xixax TV, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW139842121 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dJYazfgvQGU\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD - AUDIO</u></a>\").According to PTA, the last day of filming on <em>Phantom Thread</em> coincided with Demme’s death (Xixax TV, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW139842121 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ro9bS5A-8j8\"><u>PHANTOM THREAD - London Q&amp;A</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-20523/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:24.608253588516646,31.421949760765557,201.25897129186603,136.93331339712915"}}}]}]}]}